OL,3,CMore than 1,000 officers in one force
OL,4,Csigned off with mental health issues
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 Greater Manchester
OL,7,FPolice officers were signed off work
OL,8,Flast year due to mental health issues,
OL,9,Fa Freedom of Information request has
OL,10,Frevealed.
OL,12,FOfficers were signed off for a number
OL,13,Fof reasons including stress,
OL,14,Fdepression, anxiety or post-traumatic
OL,15,Fstress disorder.
OL,17,FThe figure at Greater Manchester
OL,18,FPolice has increased by 2% on last
OL,19,Fyear, and has jumped by 22% nationally
OL,20,Fin the financial year 2024-25.
