OL,6,F33 of the 45 forces that provided
OL,7,Ffigures both this year and last year
OL,8,Freported an increased number of
OL,9,Fofficers being signed off for mental
OL,10,Fill health.
OL,12,FMike Peake, Chair of Greater
OL,13,FManchester Police Federation, said:
OL,14,F"Policing is a vocation like no other
OL,15,F` police officers see some horrific
OL,16,Fsights and deal with more violent,
OL,17,Fstressful and traumatic incidents than
OL,18,Fever before.
