OL,3,CMore than 1,000 officers in one force
OL,4,Csigned off with mental health issues
OL,6,F"As such, it comes as no surprise that
OL,7,F1,050 Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,Fofficers were signed off work in the
OL,9,Fpast year due to mental health issues,
OL,10,Fbut what is particularly concerning is
OL,11,Fthat figure has risen once more."
OL,13,FPaul Williams, Wellbeing Lead of the
OL,14,FPolice Federation of England and Wales
OL,15,F(PFEW), said that the national figures
OL,16,Fwere "very worrying".
