OL,6,FHe said: "Behind each mental health
OL,7,Fcondition, you've got an individual
OL,8,Fwho's going through incredible trauma,
OL,9,Fwhich has a significant impact not
OL,10,Fjust on them, but on their family,
OL,11,Fmarriage and career. It can be
OL,12,Fdevastating."
OL,14,FPaul said it was "a demonstration of
OL,15,Fthe complexities of policing, a
OL,16,Fdemonstration of the budget cuts over
OL,17,Fthe past 15 years, and the lack of
OL,18,Fincrease in pay for police officers.
