OL,6,FAll this has contributed to an extreme
OL,7,Frise in mental ill health within the
OL,8,Fpolice, and it's only going to keep
OL,9,Frising if there's no intervention".
OL,11,FTo try to help officers who are
OL,12,Fstruggling with mental health issues,
OL,13,Fa new 24-hour Mental Health Crisis
OL,14,FLine on 0300 131 2789 has been
OL,15,Flaunched by The National Police
OL,16,FWellbeing Service, Oscar Kilo.
OL,18,FIt is staffed by expert counsellors to
OL,19,Fsupport those working in policing who
OL,20,Fare experiencing a mental health
OL,21,Fcrisis or suicidal thoughts.
