OL,6,FIt is confidential and completely
OL,7,Findependent ` no information will be
OL,8,Fshared with the force, Occupational
OL,9,FHealth departments or line management.
OL,11,FMike said: "Much more needs to be done
OL,12,Fto acknowledge the constant
OL,13,Fdifficulties that police officers face
OL,14,Fevery day, and I welcome the launch of
OL,15,Fthe new Mental Health Crisis Line for
OL,16,Fpolice officers and staff.
OL,18,FSuicide among police officers is
OL,19,Falarmingly on the increase, and it is
OL,20,Fmy hope that the crisis line will go
OL,21,Fsome way to address this."
